  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to assess the effectiveness of serious EUREKOI gambling on the anxiety of&#xD;
      family caregivers of patients with newly diagnosed Alzheimer's disease.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
